1. Pre-requisites – Data Foundation (Already in Place)
Your pipeline summary confirms the following are built and populated:
Vector Layer: Neo4j database with AtomicChunk nodes holding BioLORD-2023
embeddings (768-dim, cosine index atomic_chunk_embedding), connected to
ClinicalContext and Document nodes.
Knowledge Graph: Drug, Patient and other medical entities generated by
